Singer Peter Okoye of PSquare has taken to social media to berate APC governors complaining about the Naira swap policy of the Federal government. In a  series of posts shared on Instastories, Peter stated that the governors should stop complaining because Nigerians are not complaining about the policy. He claimed that Nigerians are used to the hardship inflicted on them by the APC government and are in support of the Naira swap policy despite the attendant hardship that has accompanied it. Read his post below…